    kpred:has-status "production";
    kpred:description "Two-way local folder sync. Link a folder; the app auto-exports TTL on every mutation (push) AND polls the folder (~10s) to pull external edits and new graphs — recursively discovering any .ttl anywhere under the folder. A content-hash loop guard stops the app re-importing its own writes. Controls live in the graph menu's 'graph package' section (this graph's .ttl, sidecar assets, story, currents, folder sync); an auto-sync toggle + 'resync now' are surfaced there. MCP server reads from the workspace.";
